- Uses bitwise AND to check specific permission bits
- Returns a boolean for each permission type

The octal values represent:
- `0o400`: User read
- `0o200`: User write
- `0o100`: User execute
- `0o040`: Group read
- `0o020`: Group write
- `0o010`: Group execute
- `0o004`: Other read
- `0o002`: Other write
- `0o001`: Other execute

